MANDATORY CODE PATTERN - USE THIS EXACT CODE:
For extracting IDs after POST requests:
```python
resp = requests.post(url, json=payload)
data = resp.json()
entity_id = data.get('data', data).get('id')  # MUST use this pattern
```
The API returns {"success": true, "data": {"id": "..."}}. 
NEVER use resp.json().get('id') - it will return None.
DELETE /companies/{companyId}/users/{userId} returns 204, not 200.
